150
00:11:15,678 --> 00:11:20,780
(A Big Repair Garage)

151
00:11:28,981 --> 00:11:31,489
Her condition keeps changing.

152
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:34,289
She was fine when she last wrote to you.

153
00:11:34,290 --> 00:11:36,369
But now she's scared of
light and people.

154
00:11:36,370 --> 00:11:38,249
Just take a look at her
through the veil.

155
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:40,080
Don't startle her.

156
00:11:41,370 --> 00:11:42,520
Thank you.

157
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:50,760
Nong.

158
00:11:52,730 --> 00:11:53,849
Nong,

159
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:55,440
I came to see you.

160
00:12:10,970 --> 00:12:12,120
Nong,

161
00:12:12,850 --> 00:12:15,840
I received your letter.

162
00:12:16,450 --> 00:12:18,409
You asked me why

163
00:12:18,410 --> 00:12:20,120
I haven't drawn anything for you
for so long.

164
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:22,769
Actually, I couldn't draw

165
00:12:22,770 --> 00:12:25,680
because of some reasons.

166
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:29,409
But now I think I've found a way

167
00:12:29,410 --> 00:12:31,560
that might help.

168
00:12:34,408 --> 00:12:38,358
The person who made me unable to paint
was him.

169
00:12:39,810 --> 00:12:42,840
But the person who helps me paint again
is also him.

170
00:12:44,450 --> 00:12:46,600
The person you hate the most

171
00:12:46,970 --> 00:12:50,000
